    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 1 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 13 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 1 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You coat your body with a thin layer of bodily fluids, making you slippery to the touch and gaining a +4 bonus to Escape Artist and Dexterity checks to escape bindings, as well as a +4 bonus to grapple checks to resist or break free of being grappled.</p>\n\n\n\n",
